    <section id="scholarshipIntro">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div id="intro" class="col-12">
                    <h1>Scholarships at INTO London</h1>
                        <h2><p>At INTO London, we are committed to helping ambitious international students like you achieve their goals of studying at a world-class university in the UK. With a range of generous scholarships on offer, you could be eligible to receive funding to help towards your tuition fees – regardless of your background or financial circumstance.</p>
<p>If you can’t see a scholarship that applies to you, keep checking back – this page is regularly updated with the latest information.</p>
</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
