    <section class="scholarships-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

                    <div id="qualify" class="col-12">
                        <h3>Do I qualify for a scholarship?</h3>
                        <p>To find out whether you are eligible to apply, you'll need to take a look at the requirements for each individual scholarship. If you are not eligible for one particular scholarship, there may be another you can apply for instead.</p>
<p>Please be aware that successful scholarship holders will be expected to:</p>
<ul>
<li>successfully meet all remaining conditions for entry to their chosen course</li>
<li>maintain excellent attendance and complete all work during their course</li>
</ul>

                    </div>
                                        <div id="scholarshipTypes" class="col-12">
                            <h3>What types of scholarship are available?</h3>
                                <h4>Academic Merit Scholarship</h4>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>This scholarship is for students who have achieved great results in their previous studies and are high academic achievers. You could be awarded up to 30% of your tuition fees.</p>

                                    </div>
                                <table>
                                    <tbody>
                                            <tr class="no-dots">
                                                <td><h4>Course</h4></td>
                                                <td>
                                                        <p><p>International Foundation</p>
</p>
                                                        <p><p>International Year One</p>
</p>
                                                        <p><p>Pre-Master's</p>
</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                                                                    <tr>
                                                <td><h4>Start dates</h4></td>
                                                <td><p>August 2020</p>
<p>September 2020</p>
<p>January 2021</p>
<p>April 2021</p>
<p>June 2021</p></td>
                                            </tr>
                                                                                                                            <tr>
                                                <td><h4>Eligibility</h4></td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p><p>All INTO London offer holders who can demonstrate good previous academic merit are eligible to apply for this scholarship. Students must submit a covering letter.</p>
</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <h4>Student Engagement Ambassador Scholarship</h4>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>INTO London offers scholarships to students who wish to support the Centre by becoming become an INTO London ambassador. Ambassadors get involved in Centre activities, and gain experience in a range of areas including social media, marketing activities, mentoring and country representation. You could be awarded up to 30% of your tuition fees.</p>

                                    </div>
                                <table>
                                    <tbody>
                                            <tr class="no-dots">
                                                <td><h4>Course</h4></td>
                                                <td>
                                                        <p><p>International Foundation</p>
</p>
                                                        <p><p>International Year One</p>
</p>
                                                        <p><p>Pre-Master's</p>
</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                                                                    <tr>
                                                <td><h4>Start dates</h4></td>
                                                <td><p>August 2020</p>
<p>September 2020</p>
<p>January 2021</p>
<p>April 2021</p>
<p>June 2021</p></td>
                                            </tr>
                                                                                                                            <tr>
                                                <td><h4>Eligibility</h4></td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p><p>Any student who holds an offer for a pathway course at INTO London is eligible to apply. Students must be able to demonstrate how they would be able to support the Centre as an ambassador.</p>
</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <h4>Regional Scholarship</h4>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>If you're starting an Academic English, International Foundation, International Year One or Graduate Diploma pathway at INTO London, you could be eligible for a scholarship of up to 30% of your tuition fees.</p>

                                    </div>
                                <table>
                                    <tbody>
                                            <tr class="no-dots">
