                                                <td>
                                                    <p><p>Please contact your Educational Counsellor or <a href="https://www.intostudy.com/en/admissions/meet-the-team">Enrolment Services Advisor</a> for further information.</p>
</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <h4>Art and Design Portfolio Scholarship</h4>
                                    <div>
                                        <p>Students of International Foundation in Art and Design at INTO London could be awarded up to 30% of their course tuition fees.</p>

                                    </div>
                                <table>
                                    <tbody>
                                            <tr class="no-dots">
